title: [SOLVED] 820-2936-A No green Light {corrosion under SMC}
message:
If SMC_RESET_L is high, bad SMC or corrosion under SMC.

If SMC_RESET_L is low, SMC is bad and pulling it down or U5010 is bad.

title: [SOLVED] 820-2936-A No green Light {corrosion under SMC}
message: yes smc_reset_L high corrosion under smc reballed, cleaning it's work solved thanks
